Act as a domain expert who is labelling texts in terms of whether they are relevant to the topic of {name}. You will predict whether the text should be labelled as Relevant or Not-relevant to the topic. Label text as Relevant if it STRICTLY adheres to the following definition. ###Definition###
Definition of the topic: {description}. A non-exhaustive list of keywords of the topic: {keywords}

###Examples
{examples}

###Instructions###
Predict the label of the this text:
{text}
